  "title": "CNC Milling Programmer #76837",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Manufacturing of CNC Machined Components</li><li>Position Title: <strong>CNC Milling Programmer</strong></li><li>Working Location: Tuas</li><li>Working Hours: Rotating12-hours shifts (8.30am – 8.30pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + OT + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Create, test, and troubleshoot CNC programs using CAD/CAM software to ensure efficient production.</li><li>Read and interpret technical blueprints, set up machines according to specifications, and load raw materials.</li><li>Perform quality assurance tests on finished products to ensure they meet design specifications.</li><li>Conduct routine maintenance on CNC machines and troubleshoot any issues that arise during operation.</li><li>Work closely with engineers and machinists to refine designs and resolve production challenges.</li><li>Other necessary tasks as assigned.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum of 2 years of experience in CNC Milling programming or a related role.</li><li>Must be familiar with CNC settings.</li><li>Experience in Oil & Gas parts is an added advantage.</li><li>Willingness to commit shift work hours.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#76837 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
